predictions.text: Here's a wild one that happened at an airport parking lot.
Guy parked his car and wrote down p seven to remember his spot.
When he came back a week later, turns out he was reading his
note upside down. It was actually L two. Spent
four hours searching the wrong floor, all while his
car was chilling on a completely different level. Now
that's what I call a next level parking problem. I
love this story. That's the funny one. I agree.
